to list all available network interfaces
`nmcli con show`
to connect to ethernet via the device `eno1` use
`nmcli dev connect eno1`
to disconnect `eno1` use
`nmcli dev disconnect eno1`
to list available wireless networks use
`nmcli dev wifi list`
to connect to a wireless network called `WiFi_host` use
`nmcli dev wifi connect WiFi_host password <password of WiFi_host>`
or if you want a prompt asking for the password use
`nmcli dev wifi connect WiFi_host --ask`
